<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reset Your Password</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px 20px;
            color: #333333;
        }
        .content h2 {
            color: #667eea;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        .alert-box {
            background-color: #fef3c7;
            border: 2px solid #fbbf24;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #78350f;
        }
        .reset-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 14px 40px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .reset-link-container {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            word-break: break-all;
        }
        .reset-link-container p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6b7280;
        }
        .reset-link-container code {
            display: block;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 3px;
            color: #667eea;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        .instructions {
            background-color: #eff6ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .instructions h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #0c4a6e;
        }
        .instructions ol {
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
            color: #0c4a6e;
        }
        .instructions li {
            margin: 8px 0;
        }
        .expiry-notice {
            background-color: #fee2e2;
            border-left: 4px solid #dc2626;
            padding: 12px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            color: #7f1d1d;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666666;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }
        .footer p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #667eea;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üîê Reset Your Password</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Password Reset Request</h2>
            <p>Hi {{userName}},</p>

            <p>We received a request to reset your EarnTrack password. Click the button below to set a new password:</p>

            <p style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{resetLink}}" class="reset-button">Reset Password</a>
            </p>

            <p>Or copy and paste this link in your browser:</p>
            <div class="reset-link-container">
                <p>Reset Link:</p>
                <code>{{resetLink}}</code>
            </div>

            <div class="instructions">
                <h3>How to Reset Your Password:</h3>
                <ol>
                    <li>Click the "Reset Password" button above</li>
                    <li>You'll be taken to a secure page where you can enter your new password</li>
                    <li>Create a strong, unique password (use a mix of letters, numbers, and symbols)</li>
                    <li>Confirm your new password</li>
                    <li>You'll be logged in with your new password</li>
                </ol>
            </div>

            <div class="expiry-notice">
                <strong>‚è±Ô∏è Important:</strong> This reset link will expire in {{expiryTime}}. If you didn't request this, please ignore this email and your password will remain unchanged.
            </div>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">
                <strong>Security Tips:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>Never share your password with anyone</li>
                    <li>Use a unique password for EarnTrack</li>
                    <li>If you didn't request this reset, please contact support immediately</li>
                </ul>
            </p>

            {{#if supportEmail}}
            <p>If you have any questions or concerns, please contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
            {{/if}}

            <p>Thank you,<br>
            <strong>The EarnTrack Team</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 EarnTrack. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
